      "content": "it really is. it's like i'm drowning in slow motion. and the worst part is that everyone expects me to just keep swimming, to \"resilience\" my way through it. but i'm just... i'm done. i'm so exhausted by the sheer effort of existing in this state. sometimes i think the only way to actually find any peace, any real quiet, is to just stop trying altogether. to just let go of the struggle.",
